/>\n<br />\n敘利亞<br />\n參見：敘利亞網路審查<br />\n在2011年民眾起事後，敘利亞開始採用深度包檢測封鎖VPN連接[8]，審查目標包括各種VPN協定，如OpenVPN、L2TP和PPTP。<br />\n<br />\n姐喺封到?"},{"pid":"4efc2210db105eaf7bb0ab122d2193288a54ff0a","tid":1672700,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86052695d66f349d825b3b9d7327a6474cb8cc5b","tid":1672700,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"其它Tor onion service嘅有限列表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Tor_onion_services\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_Tor_onion_services&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=09761989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Tor_onion_services</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"一鎖網黎個全境封鎖<br />\n公海都唔比出有TOR都無用"},{"pid":"04deffa7f6f6dc0f6e05d91babd29f2bd1100e59","tid":1672700,"uid":14880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b241aafaccf77d07b6d9896bacf6f49a98e3eefe","tid":1672700,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12c9c243d0bf89bd9818457fede8b3f51c80408e","tid":1672700,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"共產黨都封唔到Tor?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"VPN都封唔到封tor？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申電腦白痴9up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"佢依加行黑名單 如果有一日行白名單就真真正正intranet<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af36fd18427b876b06587f41f2f4076862fb3329","tid":1672700,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"支那封晒tor node係用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}